import { ReactComponent as MerkLogo } from './MerkLogo.svg'

import { ReactComponent as ShootingStar } from './ShootingStar.svg'
import { ReactComponent as TeamGraphic } from './team.svg'
import { ReactComponent as ChevronDown } from './ChevronDown.svg'
import {ReactComponent as CodeSnippet} from './CodeSnippet.svg'

    ChevronRight,
    Email,
    Phone,
